WEBVTT

00:02.519 --> 00:03.969
E. R.

00:04.070 --> 00:05.071
Previously on E. R.

00:05.172 --> 00:06.036
Hey, Rachel!

00:06.137 --> 00:08.708
- You search my room and private things!
- I was looking for drugs!

00:08.809 --> 00:10.891
I have a baby
with an amphetamine overdose.

00:10.992 --> 00:13.359
- Oh, God!
- She may never open her eyes again.

00:13.460 --> 00:15.493
Either she's out of the house by
the time I take that baby home...

00:15.528 --> 00:17.040
or I'm not taking that baby home.

00:17.141 --> 00:19.326
I'm afraid
it's definitely tumor re-growth.

00:20.261 --> 00:22.292
You should've been dead
a year ago, Mark.

00:22.993 --> 00:25.029
How much time?

00:27.080 --> 00:29.129
Mark died this morning...

00:30.585 --> 00:32.762
...at 6:04 a. m.

00:35.592 --> 00:37.784
The sun was rising,
his favorite time of day.

00:38.369 --> 00:41.324
E. R. 8x21 "ON THE BEACH"

00:41.502 --> 00:44.187
- You set the tone, Carter.
- What?

00:46.717 --> 00:48.376
Work on your jump shot.

00:50.000 --> 00:56.074
